                            <item xml:id="e1">
                              <desc>In the colophon (<ref target="#coloph1"></ref>), the
                            scribe <persName ref="PRS13510TaklaS" role="scribe"></persName> states that
                          he wrote the manuscript at the expense of <persName ref="PRS13511KidanaM" role="donor"></persName>
                        and his brother <persName ref="PRS13513WaldaI" role="donor"></persName>. The name of
                      <persName ref="PRS13512WalattaH"></persName> is also mentioned. The manuscript was written
                    for <foreign>ታቦተ፡ አማኑኤል</foreign>, possibly to be identified with
                    <placeName ref="INS0925Amanuel"></placeName>.</desc>
                            </item>
